      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GIFTED LILLY (1) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished in the money last time though when second (21.92) at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Can go on with it. RINGWALD (5) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Shian Peaches (22.07) in a Grade 4. Has the pace to be prominent. Good beginner but will need a little luck from a middle draw. Can feature again. JIMMY JAX (8) should enjoy clear running from the outside box. Below best latest at this track (22.87) when 8th and beaten 11 lengths. Has a strong winning record here at this journey including five wins. The form from his last run stacks up well. Key runner on best form. PANAMA LOCO (4) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.",
